# Cursor AI Rules — codecontext (Python)

## Build/Test
- `uv sync --all-extras`
- `uv run pytest -q`
- `uv run python -m codecontext -version`

## Architecture
- `src/codecontext/cli.py` — command router
- `src/codecontext/db.py` — SQLite graph persistence
- `src/codecontext/parser.py` — parsing/detection
- `src/codecontext/indexer.py` — indexing pipeline
- `src/codecontext/mcp.py` — MCP tools and servers
- `src/codecontext/llm.py` — provider abstraction
- `src/codecontext/ai.py` — AI chains
- `src/codecontext/web.py` — FastAPI routes

## Coding Standards
- Python 3.12+
- Keep CLI/MCP contracts backward compatible
- Prefer straightforward code and explicit errors
- Add/adjust tests in `tests/` for behavior changes
